# Multiplayer Rules
- Stack: Netcode for GameObjects (NGO) + Unity Transport.
- Model: server-authoritative; client prediction only where needed.
- Persistent sync via `NetworkVariable<T>`.
- RPC roles: `[ServerRpc]` for client requests, `[ClientRpc]` for server notifications.
- Validate every `ServerRpc` on server side.
- Reduce bandwidth (quantize/bit-pack; send vectors only on meaningful delta).
- Put network lifecycle logic in `OnNetworkSpawn` / `OnNetworkDespawn`.
- Never trust client-sent positions, stats, or authority claims.
